{"tid":2491082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知點解香港公廁咁污糟","createTime":"2021-04-16T05:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:40:10.000Z","uid":108894,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"98beadebe0419e94e33fb82b26460d4c09719747","tid":2491082,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"明明香港人衛生意識唔算差，城市建設又先進<br />\n但偏偏大部份公廁都超污糟<br />\n又濕又臭又黑腳印不在話下<br />\n最難頂係D馬桶，周不時一係外圍有尿，一係成個桶都係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最離譜一次直頭見過踎廁隔離地板有大pat水狀屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好幾次急到瀨屎瀨尿都唔撚夠膽入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲聽過有D治安唔好嘅地方嘅公廁會有人打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一樣野我真係百思不得其解，點解香港公廁可以差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd38fdc1c9be8b8119f33b276d8d42318235b882","tid":2491082,"uid":307619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"因為人自私"},{"pid":"a205201ce18878a18205b6a2c23a147ea7e249e3","tid":2491082,"uid":4826,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"一句講晒<br />\n外判，價低者得，請最廢既人，賺最多既錢"},{"pid":"27a768f7e2b83840336f033cadb4a49c2d7a3704","tid":2491082,"uid":317202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:22:21.000Z","msg":"因為香港人自撚私 完"},{"pid":"36502603d2fe8be48a7915258a03ad0625bf42b0","tid":2491082,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"因為香港人出名自私<br />\n咩都外判"},{"pid":"28d426706574c5ed0ae788e7fd3a58f8bb59db79","tid":2491082,"uid":134421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"睇下咩人最多用公廁咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下污糟既公廁附近咩人聚集咪知<br />\n唔見郊野d公廁污糟"},{"pid":"c5ef6084570185e5e87b942fe61660140079a2d5","tid":2491082,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36502603d2fe8be48a7915258a03ad0625bf42b0","tid":2491082,"uid":198503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"因為香港人出名自私<br />\n咩都外判"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:24:11.000Z","msg":"但照計正正常常咁沖廁<br />\n都唔會搞到咁嘅9樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19bca30e1d50e09e0cc551bc2e0c3db92cf017b","tid":2491082,"uid":125992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"污糟到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人同我一樣堅持唔喺公廁痾屎"},{"pid":"51d840261decd6d99b672d80b420bbdab0ea39e8","tid":2491082,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19bca30e1d50e09e0cc551bc2e0c3db92cf017b","tid":2491082,"uid":125992,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:24:15.000Z","msg":"污糟到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人同我一樣堅持唔喺公廁痾屎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"我有時真係太急都會衝入去<br />\n但好多時最後都唔敢痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實就算私人商場一樣都未必乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27985fca4b770db7b7af26597de7274d1bac6161","tid":2491082,"uid":72473,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T05:25:57.000Z","msg":"一來多人用但清潔少<br />\n二來廢老廢中造成，一污糟左只會再污糟落去<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，你好急尿，入到屎塔見到塊廁板上面有屎，你會唔會掂？就咁柯就算啦，結果咪越黎超越污糟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係廢中廢老開左個頭引致情況不斷惡化"},{"pid":"d5c5907824d57a3a928a3c69da2cd467748b1bcb","tid":2491082,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27985fca4b770db7b7af26597de7274d1bac